replyTime":"2019-06-01T08:49:55.000Z","msg":"可否有立法會議員代問政府，過去29年香港至少有百多萬香港市民曾經就8964民運上街「支援」學生、或到維園出席集會而會場內有標語「結束一黨專政」，根據中國《刑法》第103條第2款煽動分裂國家罪以及第105條第2款煽動顛覆國家政權罪，若「中央機構」要求香港按逃犯條例緝捕及移交觸犯該兩款條文的香港境內包括本地及外地人士，請問香港政府會否移交該人士？"},{"pid":"e93d9555eb58d5d63bc7fd96f5f4f9bb29416a17","tid":1180930,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T08:58:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f87e06f26770d72fac16856108ecc2981d3d8d","tid":1180930,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T09:00:46.000Z","msg":"如果突然發現陳同佳喺大陸殺過人都唔移交?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7286f0e71f2d5b0afad123c17ec0d9df3a8c777b","tid":1180930,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T09:45:36.000Z","msg":"台灣唔係支那一部份？<br />\n引導去支那有乜問題？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a52a68a41119e1c1973353496da5776b62c55fc","tid":1180930,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T09:48:22.000Z","msg":"保安超間接承認台灣不屬於中国？<br />\n咁應該第一個送中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f636bfd4e31c9543fee1a6dddf443e2cf5d9e6bc","tid":1180930,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T11:06:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=